### Schedule Task Application — API Collection
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/ready

### Create Email Schedule (GMT+7)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Content-Type: application/json
x-correlation-id: demo-email-001

{
  "type": "EMAIL",
  "scheduleAt": "2026-06-14T08:00:00+07:00",
  "payload": {
    "to": ["ops@internal.local"],
    "subject": "Daily report",
    "body": "Báo cáo tự động"
  }
}

### Push with Idempotency
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/push
Content-Type: application/json
idempotency-key: push-key-001

{
  "type": "FILE_READ",
  "scheduleAt": "2026-06-14T08:05:00+07:00",
  "payload": {
    "path": "sample.txt"
  }
}

### List Schedules
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules?page=1&limit=20

### Get Schedule Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}

### Cancel Schedule
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}/cancel

### Pause Cron Schedule
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}/pause

### Resume Cron Schedule
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}/resume

### Form Fill Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "FORM_FILL",
  "scheduleAt": "2026-06-14T08:15:00+07:00",
  "payload": {
    "template": { "greeting": "Hello {{name}}", "dept": "{{dept}}" },
    "data": { "name": "Alice", "dept": "IT" }
  }
}

### File Import Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "FILE_IMPORT",
  "scheduleAt": "2026-06-14T08:20:00+07:00",
  "payload": {
    "paths": ["sample.csv", "sample.json"]
  }
}

### Cron Task (08:00 daily VN time)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "EMAIL",
  "cronExpr": "0 8 * * *",
  "timezone": "Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh",
  "payload": {
    "to": ["ops@internal.local"],
    "subject": "Morning cron",
    "body": "Scheduled at 08:00 GMT+7"
  }
}
